{"word":"Hooks","slug":"hooks","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hooks</b> For tabernacle:<br/> - Made of gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=32'>Exo 26:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=37'>Exo 26:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=36&verse=36'>Exo 36:36</a> <br/> - Made of silver<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=10'>Exo 27:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=12'>Exo 38:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=17'>Exo 38:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=19'>Exo 38:19</a> <br/> In the temple, seen in Ezekiel's vision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=40&verse=43'>Eze 40:43</a><br/> Used for catching fish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=29&verse=4'>Eze 29:4</a><br/> Used for pruning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=4'>Isa 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=18&verse=5'>Isa 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=10'>Joe 3:10</a><br/><a href='S:Fleshhook'>Fleshhook</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=38&verse=4'>Eze 38:4</a>"}]}